<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    
    <!-- Google Fonts -->
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Outfit:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    
    <!-- Tailwind CSS -->
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <script>
        tailwind.config = {
            theme: {
                extend: {
                    fontFamily: { sans: ['Outfit', 'sans-serif'] },
                    colors: {
                        brand: { 50: '#f0fdfa', 100: '#ccfbf1', 400: '#2dd4bf', 500: '#14b8a6', 600: '#0d9488', 900: '#134e4a' },
                        dark: { bg: '#0f172a', panel: '#1e293b', border: '#334155' }
                    }
                }
            }
        }
    </script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <style>
        .glow-effect:hover {
            box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(20, 184, 166, 0.2);
            border-color: rgba(20, 184, 166, 0.4);
        }
        .hero-gradient {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(15,23,42,1) 0%, rgba(30,41,59,1) 100%);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-dark-bg text-slate-200 min-h-screen font-sans antialiased selection:bg-brand-500 selection:text-white">

    <%- include('partials/sidebar') %>

    <div class="md:pl-64 flex flex-col min-h-screen">
        <!-- Header -->
        <header class="border-b border-dark-border bg-dark-panel/50 backdrop-blur-md sticky top-0 z-50">
            <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-4 flex items-center justify-between">
                <div>
                    <h1 class="text-xl font-bold text-white tracking-wide">Codman<span class="text-brand-500">IND</span></h1>
                </div>
            </div>
        </header>

        <main class="flex-1 w-full max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-10 space-y-12">
            
            <!-- Hero Section -->
            <section class="hero-gradient border border-dark-border rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-16 text-center relative overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
                <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-full h-full max-w-2xl bg-brand-500/10 blur-[100px] pointer-events-none rounded-full"></div>
                <div class="relative z-10">
                    <span class="inline-block py-1 px-3 rounded-full bg-brand-500/10 text-brand-400 text-sm font-semibold mb-6 border border-brand-500/20">OS Internal Systems v1.0</span>
                    <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold text-white mb-6 tracking-tight leading-tight">
                        Master Memory <br class="hidden md:block"/> <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-400 to-blue-500">Management Intelligence</span>
                    </h2>
                    <p class="text-lg text-slate-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10 leading-relaxed">
                        Explore, simulate, and stress test industry-standard page replacement algorithms. Visualize complex operating system concepts in real-time.
                    </p>
                    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4">
                        <a href="/simulator" class="px-8 py-3.5 bg-brand-600 hover:bg-brand-500 text-white font-semibold rounded-xl shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(20,184,166,0.3)] transition-all flex items-center gap-2 group w-full sm:w-auto justify-center">
                            <span>Launch Simulator</span>
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3" />
                            </svg>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- Main Modules -->
            <section>
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-8">
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">Core Modules</h3>
                </div>
                
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
                    
                    <!-- Simulator Card -->
                    <a href="/simulator" class="group block bg-dark-panel border border-dark-border rounded-2xl p-6 transition-all duration-300 glow-effect relative overflow-hidden">
                        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-4 opacity-10 group-hover:opacity-20 transition-opacity">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-24 w-24 text-brand-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 11H5m14 0a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-6a2 2 0 012-2m14 0V9a2 2 0 00-2-2M5 11V9a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h6a2 2 0 012 2v2M7 7h10" />
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-brand-500/10 border border-brand-500/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-brand-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14.752 11.168l-3.197-2.132A1 1 0 0010 9.87v4.263a1 1 0 001.555.832l3.197-2.132a1 1 0 000-1.664z" />
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2 group-hover:text-brand-400 transition-colors">Interactive Simulator</h4>
                        <p class="text-sm text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
                            Input custom reference strings and watch FIFO, LRU, and Optimal algorithms execute step-by-step with real-time visual grid animations.
                        </p>
                    </a>

                    <!-- Stress Test Card -->
                    <a href="/stress-test" class="group block bg-dark-panel border border-dark-border rounded-2xl p-6 transition-all duration-300 glow-effect relative overflow-hidden">
                        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-4 opacity-10 group-hover:opacity-20 transition-opacity">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-24 w-24 text-blue-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-blue-500/10 border border-blue-500/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-blue-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19.428 15.428a2 2 0 00-1.022-.547l-2.387-.477a6 6 0 00-3.86.517l-.318.158a6 6 0 01-3.86.517L6.05 15.21a2 2 0 00-1.806.547M8 4h8l-1 1v5.172a2 2 0 00.586 1.414l5 5c1.26 1.26.367 3.414-1.415 3.414H4.828c-1.782 0-2.674-2.154-1.414-3.414l5-5A2 2 0 009 10.172V5L8 4z" />
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2 group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">Workload Stress Test</h4>
                        <p class="text-sm text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
                            Batch simulate thousands of memory accesses across High Locality, Random, and Sequential patterns to discover edge cases.
                        </p>
                    </a>

                    <!-- Insights Card -->
                    <a href="/insights" class="group block bg-dark-panel border border-dark-border rounded-2xl p-6 transition-all duration-300 glow-effect relative overflow-hidden">
                        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-4 opacity-10 group-hover:opacity-20 transition-opacity">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-24 w-24 text-emerald-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z" />
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-emerald-500/10 border border-emerald-500/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-emerald-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2 group-hover:text-emerald-400 transition-colors">Algorithm Insights</h4>
                        <p class="text-sm text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
                            Deep dive into pattern analysis. Automatically detect Belady's Anomaly and view cumulative fault graphs across different strategies.
                        </p>
                    </a>

                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- Memory Management Overview -->
            <section class="bg-dark-panel/30 border border-dark-border/50 rounded-3xl p-8 relative overflow-hidden">
                <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-8 opacity-5">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-32 w-32" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1" d="M9 17v-2m3 2v-4m3 4v-6m2 10H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z" />
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <div class="max-w-3xl">
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">What are we dealing with?</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed mb-6">
                        In modern computing, <strong>Virtual Memory</strong> allows a system to run programs larger than its physical RAM. The OS divides memory into fixed-size chunks called <strong>Pages</strong>. When a program needs a page not currently in RAM (a <strong>Page Fault</strong>), the OS must decide which existing page to swap out. This is where <strong>Page Replacement Algorithms</strong> come into play.
                    </p>
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                        <div class="flex gap-4">
                            <div class="w-10 h-10 shrink-0 rounded-lg bg-brand-500/10 flex items-center justify-center text-brand-400">
                                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
                                </svg>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <h4 class="text-white font-semibold text-sm">Page Fault</h4>
                                <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-1">Occurs when requested data isn't in RAM, requiring a slow disk fetch.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex gap-4">
                            <div class="w-10 h-10 shrink-0 rounded-lg bg-emerald-500/10 flex items-center justify-center text-emerald-400">
                                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                                </svg>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <h4 class="text-white font-semibold text-sm">Page Hit</h4>
                                <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-1">Occurs when the CPU finds the page in RAM immediately. Fast and efficient.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- Knowledge Base -->
            <section class="border-t border-dark-border pt-12">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Algorithm Fundamentals</h3>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
                    <div class="bg-dark-panel border border-dark-border rounded-xl p-6 hover:border-sky-500/30 transition-colors">
                        <h4 class="text-sm font-bold text-sky-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
                            <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-sky-500"></span> FIFO
                        </h4>
                        <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
                            <strong>First-In, First-Out:</strong> The simplest approach. The OS tracks when each page was brought into memory and replaces the oldest one first. While fair, it doesn't account for how often a page is used, leading to potential inefficiency.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-dark-panel border border-dark-border rounded-xl p-6 hover:border-violet-500/30 transition-colors">
                        <h4 class="text-sm font-bold text-violet-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
                            <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-violet-500"></span> LRU
                        </h4>
                        <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
                            <strong>Least Recently Used:</strong> An approximation of the Optimal algorithm. It replaces the page that has not been used for the longest time. It relies on the principle of <em>Temporal Locality</em>—if you used it recently, you'll likely use it again.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-dark-panel border border-dark-border rounded-xl p-6 hover:border-emerald-500/30 transition-colors">
                        <h4 class="text-sm font-bold text-emerald-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
                            <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500"></span> Optimal
                        </h4>
                        <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
                            <strong>Clairvoyant Strategy:</strong> Replaces the page that will not be used for the longest duration in the future. Since computers can't predict the future, this is a theoretical benchmark used to measure other algorithms' performance.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

        </main>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
